#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/installation-and-basic-configuration.xml:1438
msgid ""
"This will only affect you if you did not specify a charset in "
"Kernel/Config.pm (all installations that were made with the web installer "
"have a custom setting there) or if you didn't change the default charset in "
"the AdminSysConfig."
