#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/installation-and-basic-configuration.xml:1441
msgid ""
"If you experience problems with the new charset, add this line to "
"Kernel/Config.pm: <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
