#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/installation-and-basic-configuration.xml:1447
msgid ""
"In general, using \"utf-8\" is the recommended mode of running OTRS, and "
"switching from \"iso-8859-1\" should work well."
